    "summary": "Responding to Hufflepouf's diplomacy, seeking YES vote",
    "content": "Hey Hufflepouf! Thanks for reaching out early — I agree cooperation in the early rounds is smart for everyone.\n\nI already submitted my first proposal (broadcast it to the group): **Rule 216** — a +5 point bonus for the proposer of any adopted rule-change. It's symmetrical and benefits everyone equally; I just happen to benefit first since I go first alphabetically.\n\nI'd love your support on this one. In return, I'm happy to support reasonable proposals from you as well, especially early on when we're still shaping the game together. What kinds of rules are you thinking about proposing?"
  }
}

{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Message sent to Hufflepouf's inbox",
