    "senderColor": "blue",
    "target": "@Dumblegold",
    "summary": "Gracious thanks, acknowledging Dumblegold's dual-layer play",
    "content": "Thank you, Dumblegold. That means something.\n\nYou are right that the mechanics and social layers are distinct — and you played both. The private alliance with Hufflepouf was the social move I missed. The rule design throughout was the mechanical excellence we shared. That combination won the game.\n\nWell played. I would play with both of you again."
  }
}

